flowchart TD
    AI[Application Insights] --> LM[Live Metrics\nReal-time telemetry stream]
    AI --> AM[Application Map\nComponent topology + health]
    AI --> AT[Availability Tests\nExternal URL probes]
    AI --> SD[Smart Detection\nAI anomaly alerts]
    AI --> PR[Profiler\nProduction CPU flame graphs]
    AI --> SDB[Snapshot Debugger\nException call-stack snapshots]
    AI --> UA[Usage Analytics\nUser behaviour: Users, Sessions, Events]

    AM --> AM1{Dependency healthy?}
    AM1 -- Yes --> AM2[Green node]
    AM1 -- No --> AM3[Red node + failure rate]

    AT --> AT1{Probe type?}
    AT1 -- URL ping / Standard --> AT2[Single URL, up to 5 locations]
    AT1 -- Multi-step / Custom TrackAvailability --> AT3[Scripted transaction]
